cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use tmech in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "tmech: A C++ header-only library for compile-time tensor algebra with symbolic differentiation"
abstract: >-
  tmech is a C++17 header-only library for higher-order tensor algebra in
  computational continuum mechanics. It provides an expression-template engine
  with lazy evaluation, tensors of arbitrary rank, tensor decompositions
  (polar, eigenvalue, spectral) with derivatives, and a compile-time symbolic
  differentiation module that produces analytic tangent operators.
type: software
